</date>
) was a French political historian. Alexandre Louis Lefèbvre de Cérisy (
<date box="[380,510,1231,1256]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" value="1798" valueMax="1867">
<number box="[380,510,1231,1256]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" value="1832.5" valueMax="1867.0" valueMin="1798.0">1798–1867</number>
</date>
) was a French Lepidopterist.
</paragraph>
